race.comment: IT'S SOYSAGES (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (22.71) last time in a Mix 6/7 at this track. Tough to beat if on-song. BLACKPOOL FINN (8) was fast away from wide out with an impressive early sectional and went on to clock 22.53 in a 0.8 lengths win at this track over 390m. Should feature again. TINKER RAYS (3) is another with top-three prospects. Something for the Multiples: OLLIE REIKO (6)
